markdownRemark.html:
Cleaning out old photos and came across this.  I think the time stamp of 3.30pm is about right for a December sunset in Scotland.

I would love to go back and shoot some landscapes.  Such beauty in Scotland.  Ahh, things you don’t realise when you’re young.
